name: No One is Self-Made
description: The idea that someone is "self-made" is ridiculous. No matter where you are, what stage of success you have achieved in your life, you didn't get there on your own. "If your pride, ego, arrogance, insecurity, or ignorance keeps you from recognizing the contributions of others, then it’s time for a wake-up call. Behind every success are significant investments and contributions by some if not all of the following people: family, friends, associates, protagonists, antagonists, advisors, teachers, authors, mentors, coaches, and the list could go on." (Forbes) We are ALL ONE! Also available as a V-Neck and Tank -Screen-printed on Next Level Apparel -60% Poly / 40% Cotton blend -Made in the USA Available only at KottonZoo.
